K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423a-1: a'arya badzra bhee ra ba dh'a ra n'i n'a ma /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423a-3: 'phags pa rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi gzungs zhes bya ba //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423a-4: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423a-5: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-0: thams cad bdag la mthun par rtag tu mtha' yas pa'i dam pa'i mchog stsol bar gyur @423b cig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-1: de la nga'i rdo rje'i tshig 'di dag go //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-13: ma h'a ba la aag gri he /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-14: ha ha badzra badzra h'a ye /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-16: h'um h'um manda la sa ma ba ra aakkra bi kra me /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-24: gsang sngags thams cad kyi snying po 'di de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan sngar lan stong bzlas brjod byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-26: gsang sngags thams cad lan 'bum bzlas brjod byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-27: las gzhan thams cad kyang don yod cing thogs pa med par byed de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-28: dam tshig gsum pa'i cho ga las 'byung ba'i rig sngags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-31: gzungs thams cad kyi nang na las thams cad byed pa yin no //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-32: de nas cho ga mi bzad pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-33: rdo rje gtams pa 'dra ba ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-34: klu dang lha srin bcas pa yi //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-35: sum cu gsum lhas mi shigs pa; ;de khros pas ni lhas mchod pa'i //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-37: 'byung po kun gyis ma smad pa //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-38: de ni srung bar byed pa'i mchog /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-39: ji ltar lhar bcas 'jig rten na //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-40: sangs rgyas 'dra ba'i ston pa med //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-41: bden pa'i tshig ni de yis ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:423b-42: skye bo kun la srung gyur cig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-3: na mo ratna tra y'a ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-4: na mo badzra bhe ra wa sya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-5: ma h'a ga na ba ti sya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-14: badzra p'a ni ra nu pa l'a ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-19: ma h'a ga na pa ti la ghu la ghu /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-21: aa kra ma aa kra ma /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-24: gri h'i ta ma; damshta ma /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-26: aattra bi sha tu sha r'i ram/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-37: gur na gurna; aa bi sha aa bi sha /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-39: ma h'a badzra bhee ra we /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-40: ga na pa ti ra dzny'a pa ya ti sv'a h'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-41: cho ga la dgra thams cad rengs par bya ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-42: byad stems thams cad bcad pa la ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-43: ba'i lci ba la dkyil 'khor gru bzhi pa byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-44: sems khros pas mtshon cha la lan bdun bzlas brjod byas te sa la btsugs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-45: de ma thag tu byad stems thams cad chad par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-46: pha rol gyi dmag tshogs zlog par 'dod pas ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-47: dbyug pa la lan bdun bzlas brjod byas te de phyogs su 'phangs na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-48: dgra thams cad myos par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-49: klu dbang du bya bar 'dod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-50: khros te rdo rje la lan bdun bzlas brjod byas te bsnun na klu rnams dbang du 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424a-51: ser ba zlog par 'dod pas ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-0: rdo rje ha cang @424b ma drag bar bskor zhing sgra yang ha cang gsang mi mtho bar brjod na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-1: klu rnams ser ba mi 'bebs par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-3: chang gi rdzas rnams yungs kar la lan bdun bsngags na thub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-4: nad zhi bar 'dod pa la ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-5: nad dang mthun ba'i sman nam chu la lan bdun bsngags te 'thungs sam byungs na nad las grol bar 'gyur ro; ;las gang byed pa thams cad la'ang lan bdun bzlas brjod byas na bsam pa de 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-6: 'phags pa rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi gzungs zhes bya ba ma rungs pa phyir zlog pa rdzogs so ////
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-7: 'phags pas gsungs pa'i gzungs rnams rnam mang yang //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-8: rdo rje 'jigs byed zhal nas gsungs ba'i gzungs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-9: bsrung bya'i las bdun ldan pa'i gzungs mchog 'di //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-10: kun gyis thun mong ma yin rnal 'byor dam pa'i gzungs //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-083-023:424b-11: rnal 'byor gyi rnal 'byor chen po don yod rdo rje'i zhal snga nas bsgyur nas bod kyi bandhe skyo 'od 'byung la gnang ngo //
